com.desafio.ponto.model

Interface PontoDiaModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.liferay.portal.kernel.model.BaseModel<PontoDia>, com.liferay.portal.kernel.model.ClassedModel, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<PontoDia>, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PontoDia
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PontoDiaBaseImpl, PontoDiaImpl, PontoDiaModelImpl, PontoDiaWrapper

    @ProviderType
public interface PontoDiaModel
extends com.liferay.portal.kernel.model.BaseModel<PontoDia>
    The base model interface for the PontoDia service. Represents a row in the "ponto_dia" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

    This interface and its corresponding implementation PontoDiaModelImpl exist only as a container for the default property accessors generated by ServiceBuilder. Helper methods and all application logic should be put in PontoDiaImpl.

    Author:
    Peterson Morais
    See Also:
    PontoDia, PontoDiaImpl, PontoDiaModelImpl
